	   <tr><td colspan=2>Getting the Shadow Silk is too easy. It can be done in less than 20 min. and cost under under 10 pp. As alredy said, you can get the shadow wolf pelt in EC. Start by seeing if the Inns got some for sale. It will cost under 1pp there. If not, hunt the shadow wolf yourself (can take some time), or auction that you want to buy it. The spider silk for the Silk Swatch is also in EC and easy to get. I am a Human monk, and didnt have any problem buying the Gather Shadow Scroll in East FP at the Necro-guild. If you dont have any tailoring skills, just ask if anyone wants to combine the items for you and make the Shadow silk. I got someone to do it for me for free.<br>All in all it took me about 20 min. and costed me about 6.5 pp. So buying the Shadow Silk for over 100 pp. or so is outright stupid.&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
